<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē bhūtabāṇadyumaṇisugaṇitē māsi cāṣāḍasaṁjñē dvādaśyāṁ śuklapakṣē
<lb n="2"/>(kṣē) suragurudivasē śrīnṛsiṁhasya viṣṇōḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīmannāgasya gōtraprabhavaśubhayaśāḥ sūryya
<lb n="3" break="no"/>janyāprasūtaḥ prādāt satpuṣpamālāḥ pratidinamamalāḥ puṇyavān puṇyavṛ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dhyai <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> māhēśvararāvuttarāyaḥ śrīmānakalmāṣaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nāripeddi<unclear>r</unclear>nṛsiṁhyasya nāyakō
<lb n="5"/>bhaṁḍarūpakaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> Annamāḍadvayaṁ kṛtvā niṣkairaṣṭabhiranvahaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tadēva vētanaṁ<unclear>kṛ</unclear>tvā
<lb n="6"/>mālāyā vinivēdanē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied> datvā tapyaiṣa tatsarvvaṁ mālākāraṁ vidhāyataṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Aka
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lpayadimaṁ dharmmamākalpaṁ kalpakōpamaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">4</supplied> svāyurārōgya<unclear>yaśasāṁ</unclear> su<unclear>ka</unclear>saṁtta
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tivṛdhdhayē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pālayaṁtvaniśaṁ dharmmamimaṁ vaiṣṇavasattamāḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">5</supplied> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śāka varṣaṁbulu
<lb n="9"/>1255 gunēṇṭi Āṣāḍa śukla 12 guruvāramuna surujubhuḍujīyyana koḍku māhēśvaradāsaravu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>turāyaṁḍu tanaku puṇyamugā nāripeddi narasiṁhunāyakaprasāda kuṁcālu reṁḍu Enimidi mā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḍalu 8 ṭiki ṭhāvupaṭṭina prāsādamu Ītaḍu kuḍici tipirinarasiṁhucē vilicina tōṁṭayaṁdu puṣpavāṭika peṭṭi I
<lb n="12"/>tōṁṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ṣpālu tirumāla <unclear>beṭi</unclear> nityamu śrīnarasiṁhanāthuniki cātiṁpaṁgalāṁḍu I dharmmu Ācaṁdrārkkamugā śrīvaiṣṇavō
<lb n="13" break="no"/><unclear>tta</unclear>mula rakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī
